Cookie cutter cookies
2hrs 30min

1 c - butter
1 1/2 c - sugar
2 large eggs
1 tsp - vanilla
1 tsp - baking soda
1 tbsp - hot water
4 c - flour

Type A
Put baking soda into water
Mix all ingredients
Chill for at least 2 hours
Roll out and bake for 8-10 min at 350 degrees.
Type B
3 1/2-4c - flour
Cream butter and sugar
Then add eggs and vanilla
Add combined water and baking soda
Add flour as needed
Chill 2 hrs
Roll out and bake for 8-10 min at 350 degrees.